---
import { Navbar } from '../components/Navbar';
---

<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Mensaje Enviado - Constructora ODAP</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-gray-900 text-white flex flex-col min-h-screen">
    <Navbar client:load />

    <div class="flex-grow flex items-center justify-center px-6">
      <div class="text-center max-w-lg">
        <div class="bg-green-500 rounded-full w-24 h-24 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-green-500/50">
          <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth={2} d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">¡Mensaje Recibido!</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg mb-8">
          Gracias por contactarnos. Hemos recibido tu solicitud correctamente y nuestro equipo te responderá a la brevedad.
        </p>

        <a href="/" class="inline-block bg-yellow-500 text-black font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded hover:bg-yellow-400 transition-colors uppercase tracking-wide">
          Volver al Inicio
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
